{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, we believe that evaluating the potential of NMT in comparison to LLMs in legal contexts may provide insights in their potential, issues and evaluation approaches.",
    "Inspired by the works mentioned in the previous sections, we aim to compare the quality between two state-of-the-art LLMs and one state-of-the-art NMT system in the legal domain for four language pairs conducting both automatic and human evaluations.",
    "While there is potential for using LLMs in different ways for different tasks (e.g., with written or spoken text), this article focuses on using text-to-text LLMs for MT.",
    "Therefore, in this section we present the methodology of the study.",
    "First, we used GPT-4, the best ranked LLM at the date of writing (May 2023), according to the Chatbot Arena Leaderboard (Zheng et al. 2023)."
  ]
}